[31:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'guarantee you never delete something that\'s actually in use. Loop number 42, the Axelrod subagent arena loop. A controlled tournament where two reasoning AI agents repeatedly choose to cooperate or defect, then are compared'

[32:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with players that always make one choice. The verify being all 18 matches and 180 rounds can be reproduced from the recorded moves and fixed scoring'

[32:24] [scene:talk]
